title: Daevid Allen-Live In London (2-7-71)
description:
Daevid Allen & Friends
London, Roundhouse Feb, 7 1971

Incl. Gilli Smyh, Didier Malherbe, Christian Tritsch, Robert Wyatt, Hugh Hopper, Elton Dean, Gerry Fields....

1-Introduction-What Do You Really Want
2-Prostitute Poem-Rational Anthem
3-Poet For Sale-Jam
4-Love Is A Careless Sea
5-I Am Your Animal
6-Capt. Shaw & Mr. Gilbert-I Am Your Fantasy-Fred The Fish-Death Of Rock-Impro 

In Daevid's own words..."It was now three years since my deportation from the mum country so I was now able to legally re-enter England for the first time since 1967.
As part of this mode of return
